<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَالْكُلُّ يَسْجُدُ رَاجِيًا بَعْضَ النِّعَمْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَكْفِيهِ بَعْدَ سُجُودِهِ طُولَ الْحَيَاةِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نَجَاتُهُ مَعَ أَهْلِهِ مِنْ كُلِّ وَاشٍ وَالنِّقَمْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَالْحُرُّ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مَعْنَى الْحُرِّ عِنْدَكُمُ انْتِحَارْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلأَهْلِهِ سِجْنٌ وَذُلٌّ وَانْكِسَارْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عَارٌ غَشَاهُمُ أَيُّ عَارْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>تَعْذِيبُهُ مَا كَانَ يَوْمًا فِي زَمَانْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>الْجَلْدُ وَالتَّعْلِيقُ مِنْهُ هُوَ الْحَنَانْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَالْكَهْرَبَاءُ هِيَ اخْتِرَاعُ الْعَصْرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>شُحْنَاتٌ تُزَلْزِلُ كُلَّ ذَرَّاتِ الْجَسَدْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَيَذُوبُ فِي الأَحْمَاضِ أَهْوَنُ مِنْ سِبَاعٍ تَنْهَشُ اللَّحْمَ الْعَلِيلَ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَرُبَّمَا نَهْشَ الْكَبِدْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>